Package: kdepimlibs5
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, kdepimlibs-data (>= ${source:Version})
Description: core libraries for KDE PIM 4 applications
 This package contains PIM shared libraries needed to run KDE 4 applications.
 .
 This package is part of the KDE 4 PIM libraries module.

Package: kdepimlibs-data
Section: libs
Architecture: all
Description: core shared data for KDE PIM 4 applications
 This package contains architecture-independent PIM data files needed to run
 KDE 4 applications.
 .
 This package is part of the KDE 4 PIM libraries module.

Package: kdepimlibs5-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: kdepimlibs5 (= ${binary:Version}), kdelibs5-dev (>= 4:4.0.0-1),
 libboost-dev, libgpgme11-dev, libldap2-dev, libsasl2-dev
Conflicts: libkleopatra1-dev
Description: development files for the KDE PIM 4 core libraries
 This package contains headers and other related files needed to build KDE 4
 applications that use the KDE PIM libraries.
 .
 This package is part of the KDE 4 PIM libraries module.

Package: kdepimlibs-dbg
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Priority: extra
Depends: kdepimlibs5 (= ${binary:Version}), kdelibs5-dbg, libc6-dbg [amd64]
Description: debugging symbols for kdepimlibs
 This package contains the debugging symbols associated with kdepimlibs.
 They will automatically be used by gdb for debugging kdepimlibs-related
 issues.
